{"tid":1803280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[決戰總統立委] 電視辯論過黎，蔡英文民望應聲下跌","createTime":"2019-12-30T05:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T15:58:48.000Z","uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6ace2b3b36b5bd9f0f6aa09c5a7a1ede1541d447","tid":1803280,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T05:51:13.000Z","msg":"3%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2020總統大選倒數12天，經過昨日的總統大選唯一一場電視辯論會後，最新民調顯示，蔡賴配支持度來到45%，領先韓張配的29%，以及宋余配的7%，另外有高達41%民眾，認為蔡英文在辯論會中的表現比較好，領先韓國瑜的27%，和宋楚瑜的13%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據TVBS最新民調顯示，蔡賴配支持度來到45%，領先韓張配的29%，以及宋余配的7%，而在辯論會後，有41%民眾，認為蔡英文在辯論會中的表現比較好，領先韓國瑜的27%，和宋楚瑜的13%，然而，在28日辯論前，蔡賴配有48%的支持度，辯論後卻下降3%，另外兩個總統候選人組合皆略為下滑1%<br />\n<br />\n至於有多少選民可能會出席投票，民調發現，72.6%一定會去投票、19.3%可能會、3.8%可能不會、1.7%不會。游盈隆推估可能的投票率是70%的正負3%之間，也就是67-73%之間。<br />\n<br />\n如果明天就投票，民調發現，蔡英文、賴清德獲得52.5%、韓國瑜、張善政21.9%、宋楚瑜、余湘9.5%，未決定10.8%。<br />\n<br />\n游盈隆說，也就是明天就投票，蔡賴配將贏韓張配30.6個百分點，選舉結果將一面倒，蔡賴佩將贏得壓倒性勝利。這個差距已經是台灣選舉空前的差距。最近一次的2016年總統選舉，蔡英文在選前半個月得到46%、朱立倫21%、宋楚瑜17%左右。開票結果朱立倫56%、朱立倫31%。"},{"pid":"9c7081e01c08aef5190edfbebab5cee76c9fe17f","tid":1803280,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:00:56.000Z","msg":"懶人包：<br />\n根據民調：<br />\n<br />\n總統<br />\n蔡英文大勝<br />\n<br />\n立委<br />\n民進黨議席單獨過半<br />\n國民黨~ 40席<br />\n民眾黨~5席<br />\n時代力量：徘徊5%邊緣<br />\n<br />\n其餘小黨一律不過5%<br />\n親民黨滅黨<br />\n無黨聯滅黨"},{"pid":"b22c7c740033a410ef88ffba9a81bd77db87f97d","tid":1803280,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:05:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德國聯署有三份  呢家仲有一份未達標 <span style=\"color: red;\">最後兩日</span><br />\n<br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkTsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=6611bb21\" target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5a079ea494dcdbcdf26cf990a1d581480b519b3a","tid":1803280,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:11:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64dd8fab3f345375bb2d1d7b5df9c6744a30dac0","tid":1803280,"uid":48582,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:13:23.000Z","msg":"韓粉只信中天<br />\n死開啦TVBS"},{"pid":"42b47451dd1a5766f840f888f2c70e1dc2ed5d9c","tid":1803280,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64dd8fab3f345375bb2d1d7b5df9c6744a30dac0","tid":1803280,"uid":48582,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:13:23.000Z","msg":"韓粉只信中天<br />\n死開啦TVBS"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:14:41.000Z","msg":"其實泛藍黎講tvbs有公信力過中天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你會唔會信文匯大公d社評丫<br />\n但你會睇東方星島既新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f28a416ac0524f24a554bd295f409c96219f2b2","tid":1803280,"uid":63613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:16:59.000Z","msg":"最尾果句寫乜 9"},{"pid":"80fa1dfc198bf26321aa7dde2350d225d709c1b0","tid":1803280,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f28a416ac0524f24a554bd295f409c96219f2b2","tid":1803280,"uid":63613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:16:59.000Z","msg":"最尾果句寫乜 9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:18:10.000Z","msg":"台灣記者係咁架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢想寫蔡英文56% 朱立倫31%"},{"pid":"6987acebefab8ccdb79e35c950b04aa58db28153","tid":1803280,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:18:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"21eeb4c9eafb16b909fcb41bf571d19552f345f8","tid":1803280,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r